  "description": "<p><strong>Industry: Petrochemical </strong></p><p><strong>MNC Environment </strong></p><p><strong>Exciting career opportunity </strong><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Handle daily operational tasks and participate in plant troubleshooting</li><li>Perform field logging, routine sampling and plant testing work</li><li>Prepare process equipment for mechanical work according to SOP procedures</li><li>Carry out loading/unloading and raw material charging activities</li><li>Operates utility and process plant</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>NTC 2/Diploma holder in Chemical Process Technology</li><li>2-3 years’ experience in chemical industry preferred</li><li>2nd Grade Steam Engineer or Diploma holders with a Boiler Attendance</li><li>Certificate will have an added advantage</li><li>Experience in forklift, firefighting, confine space or work at heights certificate will have an added advantage.</li><li>Able to perform field and panel works</li><li>High awareness of job safety and housekeeping</li></ul><p>Job ID: 4RR35R45</p><p><em><strong>All Successful candidates can expect a very competitive remuneration package and a comprehensive range of benefits.</strong></em></p><p>Kindly email your resume in a detailed <strong>Word format</strong> to <a href=\"mailto:carlo@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">carlo@peopleprofilers.com</a> </p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p><p><br /><strong>People Profilers Pte Ltd</strong></p><p>20 Cecil Street, #08-09 PLUS Building Singapore 049705</p><p>+65 6950 9747   </p><p><br />EA Licence Number: 02C4944 </p><p>Registration Number: R1100011</p><p>EA Personnel: Carlo Antonio Dela Cruz</p>",
